;">全套法恩莎卫浴、五星定制纯棉床品、7年陈普洱茶、定制茶具、百年麒麟桌……自己家客厅一样舒适的一楼咖啡厅，安静的优质睡眠环境。</span></p><p style="text-indent:29px"><span style="font-family:宋体">　　苛求舒适是我们的一贯追求，品质寒舍，给懂的您！</span></p><p style="text-indent:29px"><span style="font-family:宋体">寒舍就如您一位远方朋友的家，您不会有身处异乡的感觉，来到寒舍会告诉您地道阳朔人会去吃的地方、会去玩的地方，疲倦了就回到寒舍，卸下一天的劳累蜷在一楼的沙发上静静地听着音乐……</span></p><p><br/></p>";s:4:"area";s:11:"22,349,2374";s:4:"city";s:3:"349";s:7:"address";s:14:"城北路23号";s:3:"lng";s:15:"110.50200918307";s:3:"lat";s:15:"24.785694754385";s:8:"username";s:6:"梦溪";s:7:"imglist";s:1327:"["\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171123_4520.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171124_1710.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171125_4780.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171128_3934.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171129_9043.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171131_6510.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171132_8703.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171134_4925.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171135_7606.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171137_3769.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171246_2871.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171248_9553.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171249_5913.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171251_6477.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171252_4770.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171254_8687.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171255_8805.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171257_6568.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171310_3248.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171311_5440.jpg","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171341_6773.JPG","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171404_4672.JPG","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171438_9879.JPG","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171505_6241.JPG","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171533_4558.JPG","\/Uploads\/images\/pc\/20160913\/171609_1463.JPG"]";s:7:"content";s:13:"<p>暂无</p>";s:6:"status";s:1:"2";s:11:"verify_user";s:9:"admin_hyp";s:11:"verify_time";s:10:"1473751521";s:6:"remark";N;s:9: